   to that institution.  The Author **explicitly reserves** the right to apply for
   and receive research funding, teaching-reform grants, laboratory or project support,
   or any other institutional support programs related to the Software or its
   maintenance, without such adoption constituting a waiver of these rights.

6. **Commercial use.**  Use of the Software for commercial publishing services,
   paid consulting, or proprietary products **outside** personal/institutional academic
